ta de sua publicação.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right&#58;0cm;margin-left&#58;0cm;\">&#160;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right&#58;0cm;margin-left&#58;0cm;\">&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; Roberto de Oliveira Campos Neto<br>\n&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;Presidente do Banco Central do Brasil</p>\n</div>","Voto":"52/2019-CMN","urlEdicaoItem":"/Lists/Normativos/EditForm.aspx?ID=50823","urlEdicaoLista":"/Lists/Normativos/AllItems.aspx"}]}